Based on the execution logs, here is the report:

EXISTING STRUCTURES

### Iron Production Line at (-28, -61)
Consists of following entities:
- Burner mining drill at (-28, -61) with chest at (-27.5, -59.5)
- Burner inserter at (-26.5, -59.5) 
- Stone furnace at (-25, -59) 
- Burner inserter at (-23.5, -58.5)
- Output chest at (-22.5, -58.5) containing iron plates and copper plates

### Secondary Iron Production Line at (-18, -53)
Consists of following entities:
- Burner mining drill at (-18, -53) with chest at (-17.5, -51.5)
- Burner inserter at (-16.5, -51.5)
- Stone furnace at (-15, -51)
- Burner inserter at (-13.5, -50.5)
- Output chest at (-12.5, -50.5) containing iron plates

### Coal Mining Setup at (41, -82)
Consists of following entities:
- Burner mining drill at (41, -82)
- Output chest at (41.5, -80.5) containing coal
- Burner inserter at (41.5, -79.5)

### Power Generation System
Consists of following entities:
- Steam engine at (-4.5, 12.5)
- Boiler at (-4.5, 16)
- Offshore pump at (-3.5, 27.5)
- Connected by multiple pipe groups (fluid systems 4967-4972)

### Automation Science Pack Production at (8.5, 13.5)
Consists of following entities:
- Input chest at (5.5, 13.5) containing copper plates and iron gear wheels
- Burner inserter at (6.5, 13.5)
- Assembling machine at (8.5, 13.5)
- Burner inserter at (10.5, 13.5)
- Output chest at (11.5, 13.5)
- Connected by belt groups for material transport

### Research Lab Setup
- Lab with automation science pack input
- Connected to electricity network (id 8778)

ERROR TIPS

### Power System Issues
- Ensure boiler has constant coal supply before it runs out of fuel
- Make sure steam engine is properly connected to boiler with pipes and receiving steam

### Production Line Issues
- Ensure input materials are available before starting production
- Monitor assembling machine status for ingredient shortages
- Check if inserters have proper fuel (coal) to operate

### Extraction Issues
- Cannot extract items from empty chests or chests that don't contain the specific item
- Verify item existence in chest before attempting extraction

### Space Issues
- Inserters getting blocked due to full output destinations
- Add proper item removal/sink mechanisms where items are accumulating

### Electricity Network Issues
- Machines showing "not receiving electricity" warnings
- Ensure power generation is stable and all machines are properly connected to power network
